OL,3,CJersey politician guilty of offences
OL,4,Clinked to employing Rwandan nationals
OL,6,FA Jersey politician and former
OL,7,Fminister has pleaded guilty to
OL,8,Fimmigration offences linked to the
OL,9,Femployment of Rwandan nationals.
OL,11,FDeputy Philip Ozouf appeared at
OL,12,FJersey's Royal Court on Friday 3
OL,13,FOctober 2025.
OL,15,FThe ex-minister arranged for people to
OL,16,Fwork in the island without the proper
OL,17,Fauthorisation, and was charged under
OL,18,FJersey's Immigration Law.
